1. *Divne* su ove ruže koje si mi poklonio. (These *lovely* roses you gave me are beautiful.)
2. Videla sam *divne* prirodne pejzaže dok sam bila na planinarenju. (I saw *wonderful* natural landscapes while I was hiking.)
3. Njihova kuća je zaista *divna*. (Their house is really *lovely*.)
4. *Divno* sam se provela na zabavi sinoć. (I had a *great* time at the party last night.)
5. Naša ćerka ima *divan* glas kada peva. (Our daughter has a *beautiful* voice when she sings.)
6. Bio sam u bioskopu i gledao *divan* film. (I was at the cinema watching a *wonderful* movie.)
7. Sutra nam dolazi *divna* gošća iz inostranstva. (Tomorrow we have a *lovely* guest coming from abroad.)
8. Već dugo nismo imali *divnu* priliku da se vidimo. (We haven't had a *wonderful* opportunity to see each other for a long time.)